ke":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VxkQzmD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVxkQzmD.jpg&h=6be0ee4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【人鏈】<br />\n關注組商討後決定10/9（星期二）正午十二時正開始組成人鏈，希望同學參與，路線圖如上🙏🏻<br />\n公大人注意事項<br />\n12:00準時於MC中銀對出空地集合<br />\n希望12:30可以拖好路線<br />\n人鏈的位置會因為人數再作調整<br />\n由於屬學校範圍以外，所以遇到不同政見的市民或者街坊挑釁請盡量忍耐或者尋求幫忙，大家安全為上。<br />\n服飾方面：可佩戴full gear，但盡量不要佩戴自己出去發夢嗰套，黑衣為記<br />\n現場會派發白絲帶，最好自備口罩🙏🏻<br />\n萬事小心，不見不散。"},{"pid":"83a911fc46c7d45515dfac6c57da0a0a7f1b275e","tid":1554953,"uid":23156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029a8c249a7e4aa429d3a29b1e7763ae16a735c1","tid":1554953,"uid":312464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fcb8110101e563ad6cfa865bb4462c2bbbc99b0","tid":1554953,"uid":136981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c44e80cf95eb57978c7bf77c1a735f24c60a312","tid":1554953,"uid":312464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:36:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96a986f48ae1f6e5df0c17494d2493468613d06d","tid":1554953,"uid":276979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:36:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"70636975c1d872e7cb7961316397b702cf086503","tid":1554953,"uid":136981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:47:09.000Z","msg":"上堂上到咁悶 黎拖下手仔啦"},{"pid":"cfbbfd7ea0b5e10d41e0566c93783baaa74abdf3","tid":